Shifter
The Shifter is one of the most dangerous magic-users on Rifts Earth: a
summoner who opens dimensional Rifts to draw beings from other planes,
broker deals with demons, and travel the megaverse.

Shifters command the highest starting PPE of any OCC. They can summon
and bind supernatural entities, but the risks are enormous. Playing a Shifter
requires respect for the power they wield.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 14.
PPE: Very high starting pool.
Starting equipment: Grimoire of summoning, protective wards, travel clothing,
ritual components kit, and a sidearm.
